Package: uklakes
Title: Retrieves Lake Information from UK CEH Lakes Portal
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: person("Rob", "Briers", email = "r.briers@napier.ac.uk",
  role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-0341-1203"))
Description: Retrieves a summary of the lake information from the UK CEH Lake 
  Portal for a lake or series of lakes, based on the lakeid. Can also search 
  for lakeid values based on strings in the lake name. For details of the 
  information available, see the Lakes Portal Website 
  (\url{https://uklakes.ceh.ac.uk/}.)
License: GPL (>= 3) + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
